title: Total Annihilation (portable)
description:
Total Annihilation is a real-time strategy game created
by Cavedog Entertainment. 
---------

From this great game, I tryed make small, portable, fully
independent mod. mod have small number of maps, but can be played
also on all original maps.
Not need installation. Size: 8 mb.
-------
can play Skirmish and Multiplayer mode.
tested on: Windows XP, Windows 7

P.S.
tested with, Kaspersky Virus Removal Tool (last base: 2016.5.13) 
everything is clear
